fling.compiler.api

Class APICompiler

  • java.lang.Object
    • fling.compiler.api.APICompiler
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PolynomialAPICompiler, ReliableAPICompiler

    public abstract class APICompiler
extends Object
    Encodes deterministic pushdown automaton (DPDA) as type declarations constituting proper fluent API of the automaton's language. The automaton is compiled into an AST which can be translated to any polymorphic, object-oriented language (theoretically).
    Author:
    Ori Roth
